Is Best Buy's open box and refurbished tech actually worth the savings? We went hands-on with everything from a "pristine" PS5 to mysterious AirPods that still belonged to someone named Jasper. Some deals were surprisingly good, others...well, let's just say there's a reason why that Samsung tablet was returned.
